jau secukupnya<br />\n1 bks mi telor<br />\n1 sdm minyak wijen<br />\nbawang goreng untuk taburan<br />\nCARA MEMBUAT BAKMI GORENG SPESIAL :<br />\nPanaskan minyak, tumis bawang putih dan bawang merah hingga harum lalu masukkan daging ayam. Masak hingga daging matang kemudian masukkan telur, aduk hingga telur matang.<br />\nMasukkan baso sapi, aduk sebentar, tambahkan saos tiram, kecap manis, garam, gula, merica dan tambahkan air secukupnya.<br />\nMasukkan wortel, sawi hijau, dan mie, aduk hingga matang lalu tuangi minyak wijen, aduk sebentar. Angkat dan hidangkan dengan taburan bawang goreng."},{"pid":"df8da41a64be8005a42399eb065bf6f35e83796f","tid":271951,"uid":77875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T15:53:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"197ac6e1f7ae51e8c3a674d9a265f3c6a3e9fc81","tid":271951,"uid":12458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T15:54:52.000Z","msg":"rooke marie"},{"pid":"f8205b22dbcb5683ff3dae2511b51dcf20da582e","tid":271951,"uid":19560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T16:26:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9a0e3f17a14f9b0cbcfa4cdcc68832f26444318","tid":271951,"uid":23734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T16:27:46.000Z","msg":"Tiot&eacute;"},{"pid":"4621d461d787de7d72d00d63ab95a7105d6e18aa","tid":271951,"uid":1369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T16:36:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sw5tVkJ0o6w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fsw5tVkJ0o6w&d=sCdFQRGDBylZsrJLvB35p%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=ce96090e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\